# NEMETIC STRING
# Technology_Environmental_Adaptation (C147)

Φ(TechnologyEnvironmentalAdaptation) = σ(adaptation|stasis) ∘ ρ(resilience|fragility) ∘ λ(innovation|inertia) ∘ β(collaboration|isolation) ∘ δγ(sustainability|exploitation) ∘ μ(technology|nature) + ε | :adaptive

# OPERATOR BREAKDOWN
# σ(adaptation|stasis)             :: Air  :: Perception of change vs resistance to change
# ρ(resilience|fragility)          :: Water :: Flow between robust and fragile system states
# λ(innovation|inertia)            :: Fire  :: Transformative innovation vs institutional inertia
# β(collaboration|isolation)       :: Wood  :: Growth through collective action vs isolation
# δγ(sustainability|exploitation)  :: Earth :: Grounding in sustainable practice vs extractive exploitation
# μ(technology|nature)             :: Metal :: Structural tension between technological and natural systems
